      "author": "MB-YUL",
      "description": "## What's new\n\n**Tag autocomplete** — type `[[#` and start typing; a suggestion list filtered from your vault's existing tags narrows as you type. Selecting a tag inserts `[[#tagname|` with the cursor ready for the label.\n\n**Right-click wrap** — select any text, right-click → **Wrap as inline tag**, pick a tag from the fuzzy-search modal. The selection becomes the label: `[[#tag|your selection]]`.",
